name:                transient
stack:               ( -- )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            stateless
category:            compilation, dictionary, file loading

description:         marks the header of the last word as discardable.
                     Headers of words marked as transient will be trashed
                     when loading the file they were defined in has completed.
                     This limits the scope on those words to inside the same
                     file only.

standard:            no
deviation:           standard has no equivalent
